title: Furniture Pack - Antique
description: This Victorian Furniture Pack - includes over 50 vintage props for the Old Office and Room
longDescription:
With an asset of Victorian Furniture for an old vintage office or room, you can easily create an atmospheric vintage style location! This Victorian set includes these vintage props: Chairs, tables, cabinets, rugs, books, clocks and nightstands.


YouTube video: https://youtu.be/sBRpI6w5uvE


If you are creating a vintage location and need antique props for the location! This Victorian furniture asset is the best option for you!
technicalDetails:
Features:

  • More than 50 objects
  • Modular
  • High-Quality props
  • Scene included
  • PBR
  • Atlased textures


Number of Meshes: 51

Collision: Yes

Vertex Count: Varied 4 to 9528

Number of Materials: 39

Number of Textures: 76

Texture Resolutions: 4096*4096

Information in the LOD (number, number of levels) = not used.
